creator: Livehouse
descriptionHtml:
Livehouse is - All Live groups in your hand.
Friends, Classmates, Family, Teams, Games, Events, they are all in Livehouse Groups.
In Livehouse, making new friends & keep in touch with them:
the whole internet in your Livehouse app.


FEATURES:
Discover live groups — Discover thousands of Livehouses and Livevoices(audio groups) covering trending topics. Go online anytime to chat with the people you like, or hop in as watcher and listener to see and hear what others are talking about.

Group chat & voice chat for free — Enjoy free chatting in Livehouse over 3G, 4G, or Wi-Fi.

Party with friends — Group voice talk with friends no matter where they are. You can share your stories, broadcast your favorite musics, sing karaokes, and play a range of games such as Among Us & Roblox together directly in LiveVoice with people you like.

Share and follow — Share your favorite Livehouses and Livevoices on Facebook, Twitter, Instagram, Snapchat and other social media. Follow them, make new friends in Livehouse.
descriptionShort: Livehouse is a social platform that helps people to find live groups and friends

title: Livehouse-Make Friends Fast!

creator: Livehouse
descriptionHtml:
Livehouse is the best way to share the moment with your friends.
In Livehouse, you can do a live audio or live streaming, post your funny ideas or stories from your daily moments, and share what's new with your friends and communities. You can do all of these on Livehouse anytime and anywhere.
If you want to build your own community or group, Livehouse is perfect for you. You can create your group in seconds and live chat with your friends/fans.

Share your moments:
- You can do live audio or live video anytime and anywhere for free.
- Posts videos or photos to your moment that will show on your profile to share your life with your friends.
- Explore what's new from other people's Live and make new friends.
Find Your Groups/Communities:
- Discover thousands of chat rooms and audio rooms covering trending topics. Are you a gameholic and want to find someone plays Roblox or Minecraft? Or are you part of a school sports team? Livehouse helps you find the right groups.
Build Your Groups/Communities:
- You can start building your own community in Livehouse. It's super easy and fast. Start building your great group to attract more people to join.
- If you are an influencer and want to build your own fan group, Livehouse is perfect for you. Start building your exclusive fan group. Livehouse is a great way to engage your fans.
Stay connected with your Friends
- Stay in touch with friends and groups with live messaging and stories.
- With live audio and video chatting, you can chat with your friends anytime, anywhere.

Follow us to get the latest news, updates and events:
- Tiktok: https://tiktok.com/@livehouseapp
- Facebook:https://www.facebook.com/livehouseapp/
- Twitter: https://twitter.com/LivehouseApp
- Official website：https://www.livehouse.social/
You are welcome to send your feedback and suggestions to us:
livehousetech@gmail.­com

title: Livehouse - Go Live in Groups

creator: Livehouse
descriptionHtml:
Livehouse is a cool way to hang out with your friends. We redefined conversation. Making it super easy for you to connect with your friends and family.

Go Live with Friends:
- Stay in touch with your friends by starting a Live anytime and anywhere.
- Play games together, watch videos together, group chat together. Sharing every moment with your friends.

Communities and Groups:
- In Livehouse, you can make a home for your communities and friends.
- Whether you’re part of a school club, a gaming group like Roblox, Fortnite, Call of Duty, an influencer wants to build your own fan group or just friends that want to spend time together. You can build a Livehouse to talk every day and hang out more often.

Stay connected with your Friends
- Stay in touch with friends through live messaging, voice chat and video chat. Or share your day with stories.
- With Livehouse creative chatting tools, conversation has never been cooler :p
